<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Unchanged </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, October 4 (Xinhua) -- The general price index on Tehran
Stock Exchange closed at 1535.56 points on Sunday, unchanged from
Saturday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 3,096,882 shares changed hands in 862 deals, and the
turnover stood at 11.23 billion rials (about 2.04 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 46 companies made gains and those of 16 others
declined. 
</P>
