<HEADLINE> Uganda Condemns Sudanese Air Attack </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, October 4 (Xinhua) -- The Ugandan government
condemned the Sudanese air attack on Pakele trading center in the
northwestern district of Moyo district.
</P>
<P>
