increase to rapid economic growth. Statistics show that the local
gross domestic product for the January-August period hit 117.3
billion yuan (14.13 billion US dollars), up by 9.5 percent on the
previous year's period. Per capita monthly wages rose by 13.2
percent to 927.5 yuan.
