million U.S. dollars) and next year it will offer 133 million baht
(3.41 million dollars), Monday's Bangkok Post quoted Sumathee
Srisuchart, deputy director general of the Department of Technical
Economic Cooperation (DETEC), as saying. (Thailand-Aid)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
