HEFEI, October 5 (Xinhua) -- China's Anhui Province has made
an effort to develop export-oriented agriculture by
introducing advanced agricultural technology and increasing
agricultural product exports.
</P>
<P>
A provincial Agriculture Bureau official says that, since 1978,
exports of agriculture products have increased by 16.9 percent
annually. The agriculture sector in Anhui has attracted 400
million U.S. dollars worth of investment, and exported over 700
agricultural products.
</P>
