BAGHDAD -- A Palestinian living in Iraq broke into a synagogue
of Iraqi Jews Sunday morning and killed four people, including two
Jews,
</P>
<P>
The official Iraqi News Agency (INA) reported the Iraqi
cabinet, under the chairmanship of President Saddam Hussein,
convened an urgent session on Sunday evening to discuss the
incident. (Iraq-Palestinian-Jew) 
</P>
